    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305370/extras/a8733c7adab885ee47f1bbbd46326790.avif?t=1770113484\" width=780 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305370/extras/0d8db6bf60f33101e2a0d7f9a5ac75af.poster.avif?t=1770113484\" width=780 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305370/extras/0d8db6bf60f33101e2a0d7f9a5ac75af.webm?t=1770113484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305370/extras/0d8db6bf60f33101e2a0d7f9a5ac75af.mp4?t=1770113484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“约翰和珊买下了废弃的农场，全新的生活在这里开始。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是风来之国的平行时空。约翰和珊买下了废弃的农场。全新的生活在这里开始。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《风来之国》的大型DLC，全新的故事，全新的游戏模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305370/extras/75087fc10cdc1f75b9a4f65570b3dd0c.avif?t=1770113484\" width=780 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305370/extras/878b7202c7fe93d065bd5ee239e106e3.avif?t=1770113484\" width=780 height=215 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >命运在未知的角落发生了偏差。这个风来之国没有灾难，没有危险。困难无法阻止对快乐和幸福的追求。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305370/extras/5e621abf018b01281d0dcda10e1de39e.avif?t=1770113484\" width=780 height=90 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305370/extras/fc9375c6a372b2e1f41ab4483e8be20f.avif?t=1770113484\" width=780 height=215 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打理属于你的农场。钓鱼，矿坑，一样不少，但都是全新的玩法。伙伴，动物，甚至幽灵都会加入你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305370/extras/8552017eaf4429be9461db0567499ac1.avif?t=1770113484\" width=780 height=90 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305370/extras/4bbc5d02acf64c600896ce3b21b7a6c0.avif?t=1770113484\" width=780 height=215 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全新的料理系统，更多材料，更多菜谱。从种子开始，亲手完成。这些都记录在约翰的料理笔记中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305370/extras/34c5fc30dac3179752fa0b4427a5919a.avif?t=1770113484\" width=780 height=90 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305370/extras/a4124e9eb28f9d06fb6cf80efbbaed4e.avif?t=1770113484\" width=780 height=215 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让废墟重返往日的光辉。和伙伴们一起，让这里成为我们的海鸥镇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305370/extras/56687c92a54b6efcd030cb2c0df4ef9c.avif?t=1770113484\" width=780 height=105 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305370/extras/854a5077485ba575405de6cf4f9cb4c8.avif?t=1770113484\" width=780 height=215 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >熟悉的角色一一登场，不过有些不一样。没有苦难，不再分离，一起为了一口美食高兴，为了一个目标努力。是时候来重新认识他们了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有慕名而来的美食家；当然也少不了追寻美景的旅人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有很多秘密等待被发现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>此内容需要在 Steam 上拥有基础游戏 Eastward 才能畅玩。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305370/extras/9eb1c5ce0e468abaf8bad025d458149c.avif?t=1770113484\" width=780 height=98 /></span></p>",
